WEBVTT

00:06.427 --> 00:09.132
Don't stay away is a widely known Negro spiritual.

00:10.314 --> 00:14.562
Oh, Santa, don't stay away.

00:15.484 --> 00:19.491
Oh, Santa, don't stay away.

00:20.453 --> 00:24.621
Our Savior saved his room enough.

00:24.955 --> 00:28.699
Room enough in the heaven for us all.

00:29.600 --> 00:33.484
Our Savior say, there's room enough.

00:34.045 --> 00:36.988
Don't stay away.

00:38.409 --> 00:43.294
Negroes on the chain gangs change the words to suit their environment and sins.

00:44.916 --> 00:49.081
Chicken Stila, don't stay away.

00:49.721 --> 00:54.186
Chicken Stila, don't stay away.

00:54.520 --> 01:02.413
Our cap'n say there's room enough, room enough in the tent for us all.

01:03.314 --> 01:11.247
Our cap'n say there's room enough, don't stay awake.

